<opener><address><addrLine>45 Albert Road</addrLine>
<addrLine>Glenageary</addrLine></address> <dateline><date>14th June/16</date></dateline> <salute>Dear Mrs. O'Rahilly</salute></opener> <p>It is only now - after this <lb/>long lapse of time - that I <lb/>can bring myself to try and <lb/>tell you how I have felt and <lb/>prayed for you ever since <lb/>I knew that a mere letter <lb/> of sympathy could only be <lb/> poor comfort in such trouble
        
    

    
         
        <pb n="2738" facs="#L1916_1055_img_2738"/>
        
        
           
            <lb/>as yours. To say nothing  <lb/>of your irreparable loss <lb/> the anxieties of Easter  <lb/>Week must have been <lb/>appalling, but please God  <lb/>you will soon have a great -  <lb/>if not <hi rend="underline">the</hi>greatest - consolation.</p> <p>Perhaps some time, later <lb/> on, you could find me some <lb/> small memento - a prayer book <lb/> or any little belonging of  <lb/>your wonderful &amp; heroic <lb/> husband - that is if you <pb/>  <lb/>can spare it to one with <lb/> so small a claim as I have.</p> <p>I wish I had known of  <lb/>the Requiem at Donnybrook. <lb/> I only heard of it yesterday <lb/> or I should have been present, <lb/> but indeed I suppose it is <lb/>he who is praying for us <lb/>in poor distracted Ireland.</p> <p>I am waiting a few years  <lb/>for L. Derg, so we may do it <lb/>together again.</p> <p>I suppose you would not
        
    
         
        <pb n="2739" facs="#L1916_1055_img_2739"/>
        
        
           
            <lb/>care to see me (?) but I am  <lb/>very often in your neighbourhood <lb/> I go up constantly to  <lb/>Lansdowne Road as my mother  <lb/>has been laid up for the past  <lb/>2 months with phlebitis. <lb/>Thank God she is now getting <lb/>better and will soon I hope <lb/> be able to get away for a <lb/>change.</p> <closer><salute>With renewed &amp; deepest  <lb/>sympathy <lb/>I remain dear Mrs O'Rahilly <lb/>Yrs ever most sincerely</salute> <signed>Amelia Jephson</signed></closer>
        
    
                </body>
            </text>

        
            
        
            
        
            
        

         

